snippet.title: Skills Matter (formerly YOW! Conferences)
snippet.description:
With 100,000+ members from 126 countries and growing, Skills Matter is the global community for Software Professionals.

Our tech community is built on a simple but powerful truth: we learn better together. 

We believe that the community ecosystem is the best tool to help developers and engineering teams share ideas, break down barriers and discover new ways of solving common challenges.

Every day our members connect on our platform and participate in expert-led talks, conferences, meetups and workshops. Skills Matter is where software professionals go to get inspired, connect with peers and learn about new technologies; and where tech experts go to share their knowledge.
